  schema:name "Accountability Tracing in Multi-Agent Systems" ;
  schema:description "Following the delegation chain from an action back to who bears accountability. The difference between responsibility (you caused it) and accountability (you answer for it), and why that distinction matters when LLM agents make mistakes." ;
